Cell["\<\
Method -> \"ShortestPathExtension\" enumerates simple paths via a recency-lex \
frontier sweep; default ShortestPathWindow K = 2 excludes triangle shortcuts.\
\
\>", "CodeText",ExpressionUUID->"dffd4478-affc-4e4a-95a0-f212b7a9324e"],

