Cell["\<\
Method -> \"CurvatureMinimizing\" traces the rope being pulled tight by \
Forman-Ricci edge curvature.\
\>", "CodeText",ExpressionUUID->"26d6ecd5-2af3-4c95-aa5f-04276786c109"],

